        {# ── WHAT IS OFF THE CUF ── #}
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="section-heading-icon" aria-hidden="true">🎉</span>
            <h2>What is Off the CUF?</h2>
            <span class="section-heading-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>

        <div class="card-content-with-image">
            <div>
                <p>Off the CUF is a relaxed and friendly morning gathering that takes
                place on the first Saturday of every month. It is open to absolutely
                everyone &mdash; whether you are part of our congregation, curious
                about church, or simply looking for some company and a good brunch.</p>

                <p>We gather in an informal café-style setting to explore a theme that
                speaks to our shared human experience. We introduce different
                perspectives, including Christian viewpoints, creating space for open
                conversation where we can listen, share, and learn from each other.</p>

                <p>Topics explored in the past include: Joy, Global aid, Peace, Olympic
                inspirations, God's love.</p>

                <p>There is no programme to follow and no pressure. Come along, grab a
                drink, have some food, and see where the morning takes you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-image">
                <div class="photo-placeholder content-image-medium">
                    <img src="/assets/images/OffTheCUFPoster.jpg" alt="Off the CUF poster" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

